<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Microsoft Visual Studio 2008 Service Pack 1 (KB2538241)</Title><Description>A security issue has been identified leading to MFC application vulnerability in DLL planting due to MFC not specifying the full path to system/localization DLLs.  You can protect your computer by installing this update from Microsoft.  After you install this item, you may have to restart your computer.</Description><UninstallNotes>This software update can be removed via Add or Remove Programs in Control Panel.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=216801</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>